EHF's new #COVID19 #vaccine survey in Texas: Democrats (52%), Texans>65 yrs old (49%), college grads (48%) & people w/ higher incomes (46%) were the groups with the highest percentage who said they are "very likely" to get a #vaccination.

Full report: https://t.co/x6P0OHcRNH https://t.co/sLelECv2tv
